{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c74d638f02","title":"中央关于新区实行土地改革的方针的指示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"119e85e050","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":12,"articleId":"c74d638f02"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7498c878f7","type":"title","text":"中央关于新区实行土地改革的方针的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c74d638f02"},{"id":"3fe65548e9","type":"paragraph","text":"晋绥分局，并告西北局、华南分局、华东局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c74d638f02"},{"id":"9f29d020e5","type":"paragraph","text":"申寝电悉。今后在新区实行土地改革，应采取“中间不动两头平”的方针。这较之过去实行的“原则上不动中农”的方针，是更明确的保障了中农（包括富裕中农在内）利益不受侵犯，更符合于巩固团结中农，顺利完成土改，并使农村生产更少受破坏影响。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c74d638f02"},{"id":"7aacb40842","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央酉文","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c74d638f02"}],"page":{"id":"1c21396644","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c74d638f02","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}